Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't able to transmute a single thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Armony!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I be so helpless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't I do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I so powerless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Armony's?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You must hate me by now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's silly. How could I hate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to talk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear, you may not have realized this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have always loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I cared for you more than\Nanyone else ever could.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:02:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter what I tried,\NI just couldn't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what would make you the happiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What I could do to make\Nmy daughter happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, you're so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew. I always knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm your daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and daughters always know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your daughter, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly girl, of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I guess we're both silly then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like father, like daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Armony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy. You big dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see?\NWere they smiling, Edward?
